    $
      &P{S^2 <= 1.6664 | sigma^2 = 4} \
      =& P{(15 S^2) / 4 <= (15 times 1.6664) / 4} \
      =& P{chi^2 <= 6.249} approx 0.0247
    $
  ]

  *(3)* 对于 *(1)* 代入得：
